        <num>12-3-220</num>
        <content>
          <p>Any action to declare, protect, or enforce any rights or duties under this part, brought in the courts of the state, shall be brought in the Superior Court of DeKalb County, Georgia; and any action pertaining to validation of any bonds issued under this part shall likewise be brought in such court, which shall have exclusive original jurisdiction of such actions.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1958, p. 61, ยง 27; Ga. L. 1959, p. 333, ยง 3.)</p>
